commit.message:
Extract connection initialization and wrap HTTP errors (#176)

* Remove duplicate User-Agent setting

* Split Faraday middleware

Split into two middlewares, so separate Acme features that are specific only to the Acme connections.

* Extract connection initialization

* Clear legacy

* Remove extra spaces

* Revert "Clear legacy"

This reverts commit d5f5597cad6023ec91577abf695e90ea41d283e5.

* Fix rubocop

* Retry middleware be before Acme middleware

* Add tests for timeouts

* Rely on the baseline/shared error handler

* Fix rubocop

* Make it compatibile with Faraday 1

* Fix rubocop
